      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，执行器控制器放在Controllers层。服务层我打算放一个MQTT代理，叫IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker，负责设备间通信。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Services",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我把Services层加上MQTT Broker。那仓储层呢？也是ActuatorController吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Repositories",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，仓储层同样用IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController，表示数据持久化的接口。领域模型层放IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic，这是核心的PLC逻辑。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Repositories",
        "DomainModels",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我注意到MQTT Broker在多个地方出现。除了Services层，是否还需要DTOs层和Patterns层也引用它？这样设计模式和安全配置可以复用同一个组件。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DTOs",
        "Patterns",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker"
