      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以，DTOs层放IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker作为数据传输对象，Patterns层也用它体现设计模式的应用。另外再加一个Security层，放IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic做安全控制。",
      "elements_involved": [
